All Implemented Interfaces:
ICloneable, IDirtyable, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>
public class MVCHashSet<E>
extends HashSet<E>
implements ICloneable, IDirtyable

A HashSet that implements ICloneable and IDirtyable for use with AbstractDirtyableModel. Unlike the proper implementation of IDirtyable, this class will only keep track of if the set is dirty or not, it will not revert changes. TODO implement reverting changes, saving, etc

Author:
Daniel Murphy
